	<table class="mapping" id="lang_ids">
		<caption class="flush"><b>IDs of the languages for the language choice</b>. The ID should be an ISO 639-1 code. Every language must be supported in the translations provided by the backend (i.e. in the dictionary <i>glosses</i> of the data access object <i>dao.glosses</i>). The language with status <i>default</i> is chosen for requests which do not specify the language.</caption>
		<thead>
			<tr><th>id</th><th>status</th></tr>
